window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I hated her before I even knew her name.</b></p> <p>My bride. The daughter of my enemy. She's nothing more than a part of my revenge.</p> <p>I'm the one who holds her life in my hands. As well as her body. And soon, her very will. Yet, she refuses to break.</p> <p>This woman disarms me, not with weapons but with words. And not with a fist, but with a simple kiss. But a match made in hate can have no other ending except war.</p> <p><i>This is book one in the Dark &amp; Dirty Vows series which is intended for mature listeners. Welcome to the dark side...</i></p>"; 
